tfolio snapshot people company overview harding loevner funds inc  global equity portfolio is an openended equity mutual fund launched and managed by harding loevner lp it invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it invests in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization the fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed financially sound fast growing and strongly competitive to create its portfolio it benchmarks the performance of its portfolio ag harding loevner funds inc  global equity portfolio is an openended equity mutual fund launched and managed by harding loevner lp it invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it invests in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization the fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed financially sound fast growing and strongly competitive to create its portfolio it benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the msci all country world net index the fund conducts proprietary research to make its investments harding loevner funds inc  global equity portfolio was formed on december   and is domiciled in the united states detailed description  crossing boulevardfourth floorbridgewater nj united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwhardingloevnercomproductsusmutualfundsglobalequityportfolio key executives for harding loevner funds inc  global equity portfolio mr peter j baughan cfa portfolio manager mr ferrill d roll portfolio manager mr christopher mack cfa portfolio manager mr richard 